HerBibleApp Verse Explanations (en-mh)
========================================

These per-verse explanations were written specifically for HerBibleApp.
The text is original devotional / interpretive commentary on the KJV
English Bible. It is © 2026 HerBibleApp; all rights reserved.

The KJV Bible itself, on which these explanations comment, is in the
public domain.

This corpus is distributed alongside the HerBibleApp client at:
  https://github.com/sangchy1972/pd-text-corpus

If you would like to use these explanations outside the HerBibleApp
client, please contact support@everlandapps.com first.
